title: Handbook of Plastic Films
description:
Handbook of Plastic Films (2003).pdf

ISBN: 1-85957-338-X

Plastic films are high-performance materials which play an essential part in modern life. Plastic films are mostly used in packakging applications but as will be seen from this book they are also used in the agricultural, medical and engineering fields. The understanding of the nature of plastic films, their production techniques, applications and their characterisation is essential for producing new types of plastic films. This handbook has been written to discuss the production and main uses of plastic films
